modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_LOW_ENERGY: 戰甲的能量上限降低為四分之一，並且能量恢復速率也會大大降低。
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_IMPACT: Enemies can deal enhanced impact damage. Finishing damage is not resisted.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_SLASH: Enemies can deal enhanced slash damage. Finishing damage is not resisted.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_PUNCTURE: Enemies can deal enhanced puncture damage. Finishing damage is not resisted.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_EXIMUS: Eximus units have a much higher spawn rate in this mission. Some of their auras stack.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_MAGNETIC: Enemies deal increased Magnetic damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_CORROSIVE: Enemies deal increased Corrosive damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_VIRAL: Enemies deal increased Viral damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_ELECTRICITY: Enemies deal increased Electric damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_RADIATION: Enemies deal increased Radiation damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_GAS: Enemies deal increased Gas damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_FIRE: Enemies deal increased Heat damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_EXPLOSION: Enemies deal increased Blast damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_FREEZE: Enemies deal increased Cold damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_TOXIN: Enemies deal increased Toxin damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_POISON: Enemies deal increased Toxin damage and also have increased Immunity to said damage type.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_HAZARD_RADIATION: Any damage received will impart radiation effects, and so will green clouds around the tileset.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_HAZARD_MAGNETIC: Reduced Gravity. Blue blobs that deal magnetic procs placed through out the tileset.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_HAZARD_FOG: Limited visibility in the tileset due to dense fog. Forced night cycle on planets like earth.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_HAZARD_FIRE: The tileset has a fire hazard. Warframe health is halved. Meltdown Iminent.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_HAZARD_ICE: Maximum Shield Capacity is halved. Ice patches that cause cold procs.
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_HAZARD_COLD: 行動能力大幅下降。此模式的衝刺功能已被禁用。
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_ARMOR: 敵人已有強化護甲，腐蝕觸發效果將減半
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_SHIELDS: 敵人已有強化護盾，建議使用磁力元素。
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_SECONDARY_ONLY: 此任務中只能使用次要武器，其他類型的武器將會自動被換掉
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_SHOTGUN_ONLY: 此任務中只能使用霰彈槍，其他類型的武器將會自動被換掉
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_SNIPER_ONLY: 此任務中只能使用狙擊槍，其他類型的武器將會自動被換掉
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_RIFLE_ONLY: 此任務中只能使用突擊步槍，其他類型的武器將會自動被換掉
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_MELEE_ONLY: 此任務中只能使用近戰武器，其他類型的武器將會自動被換掉
modifierDescriptions.SORTIE_MODIFIER_BOW_ONLY: 此任務中只能使用弓箭類武器，其他類型的武器將會自動被換掉
